  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [ ] Foundry\n- [ ] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\n_No response_\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating System\n\n_No response_\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nnext nonce, if not set in tx, is always on chain + 1.\r\n\r\nthis will result in invalid tx if there's already a tx with on chain nonce + in the pool.\r\n\r\nnext nonce should be `max(pending, on-chain) + 1`,\r\n\r\nalternatively, it could also be the highest nonce that's not currently pending in the pool ",
